nodes.text: Kethmandi was a planet in the galaxy. Sometime between 19 BBY and 10 BBY,[source?] Chewbacca was an Imperial prisoner on Kethmandi.

Kethmandi was first mentioned in Solo: A Star Wars Story: A Junior Novel. In the non-canon television series LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars, Kethmandi is a rocky, forested planet, and according to Pace Freemaker, it was worse than Corellia.
